name: Canny Road
overview:
Our goal is to help companies find the one or two most important pieces of information every day in the mountains of reports they have access to.

We do this by automatically consolidating, analyzing, and prioritizing all your information in your Google Analytics, Facebook Insights, and other sources and boiling the information down to the most important- and actionable- items. Then we send them to you in a customized email report which changes everyday based on the most important insights we have found about your site.
